name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Webrowse - sync tabs with your teammates!
name.zh_CN: Webrowse - 和他人协同分享浏览器窗口

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Cobrowse any website with your teammates!
short.zh_CN: 与他人快速高效地分享任何窗口

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Webrowse helps your team easily collaborate via a shared browsing window during your online meetings. Webrowse is based in chrome, and so regardless of the meeting platform you use, you and your team can easily collaborate inside Chrome. No more sendings links via zoom chat or email during a meeting, everyone can now work together in the shared window created by Webrowse.
